{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013ERsWZkG2yvE6vxv93jWEF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here is the migration report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** `Spring Boot + JoinFaces` -> `Jakarta EE 10 (WildFly 31.0.1)`\n- **High-level actions:**\n  1. Replaced all Spring Boot dependencies with single Jakarta EE 10 API dependency\n  2. Replaced Spring DI annotations (`@Component`, `@Service`, `@Autowired`, `@Configuration`) with CDI equivalents (`@Named`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject`)\n  3. Replaced Spring Data JPA `JpaRepository` interface with manual JPA `EntityManager`-based repository\n  4. Replaced Spring `@Transactional` with Jakarta `@Transactional` (JTA)\n  5. Created standard Jakarta EE WAR structure with `web.xml`, `beans.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `faces-config.xml`\n  6. Added JAX-RS REST endpoints for programmatic access and smoke testing\n  7. Migrated Dockerfile from Spring Boot embedded server to WildFly application server\n- **Overall outcome:** **SUCCESS** - All 11 smoke tests pass, application builds, deploys, and runs correctly\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Spring Boot dependencies with Jakarta EE 10 API\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with WildFly 31.0.1 on Ubuntu Noble\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/Application.java: JAX-RS activator (was Spring Boot main)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/ServletInitializer.java: Empty placeholder (was Spring WAR init)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/config/JsfConfig.java: Empty placeholder (was Spring JSF config)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/config/SpringConfig.java: Empty placeholder (was Spring config)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/entity/Contact.java: Added @Table annotation\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/repo/ContactRepository.java: JPA EntityManager-based (was Spring Data JPA)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/service/ContactService.java: CDI @ApplicationScoped (was Spring @Service)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/web/ContactController.java: CDI @Named/@SessionScoped (was Spring @Component/@Scope)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Replaced with comment (no longer used)\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/rest/ContactResource.java: JAX-RS REST endpoints\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit config\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI bean discovery config\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Servlet and JSF config\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml: JSF resource bundle config\n- src/main/webapp/index.xhtml: JSF index page (copied from resources)\n- src/main/webapp/template.xhtml: JSF template (copied from resources)\n- src/main/webapp/contact/*.xhtml: CRUD pages (copied from resources)\n- src/main/webapp/resources/css/jsfcrud.css: Stylesheet (copied from resources)\n- smoke.py: 11 smoke tests covering REST API and JSF pages\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration documentation\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-16T22:20:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure: 8 Java files, Spring Boot + JoinFaces + JSF\n[2026-03-16T22:22:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml: removed Spring Boot, added Jakarta EE 10 API\n[2026-03-16T22:24:00Z] [info] Migrated all 8 Java source files from Spring to Jakarta CDI/JPA/JAX-RS\n[2026-03-16T22:25:00Z] [info] Created REST API resource (ContactResource.java) for smoke testing\n[2026-03-16T22:26:00Z] [info] Created Jakarta EE config files: persistence.xml, beans.xml, web.xml, faces-config.xml\n[2026-03-16T22:27:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile: multi-stage build with WildFly 31.0.1\n[2026-03-16T22:28:00Z] [warning] CentOS 7 WildFly image lacks Python 3; switched to Ubuntu Noble base\n[2026-03-16T22:29:00Z] [info] Created smoke.py with 11 comprehensive test cases\n[2026-03-16T22:30:00Z] [info] Docker build succeeded (no compilation errors)\n[2026-03-16T22:32:00Z] [info] WildFly started successfully, WAR deployed at /address-book\n[2026-03-16T22:35:00Z] [info] All 11 smoke tests passed: REST API + JSF pages verified\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 1 warning (Docker base image), 0 critical errors\n- **Warning:** Initial WildFly Docker image (CentOS 7) lacked Python 3 for smoke tests. Resolved by using Ubuntu Noble base with manual WildFly installation.\n- **No manual intervention required.** Migration is complete and fully functional."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":459,"cache_read_input_tokens":118484,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":459,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1374},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1d77b2ee-6e15-42d9-9f65-0c272b9a6995","uuid":"c84f0d95-a1e8-41b0-9581-988dac67f0a7"}
